AIM:
To demonstrate the Registry editing using native tools of OS.

PROCEDURE:

Step 1: Open Command Prompt and type regedit.
Step 2: Go to HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Control Panel\Desktop import random
		
 

Step 3: Choose any Image from File Explorer and Copy its Path.
Step 4: Now Return to the Registry editing tool and Right Click on Wallpaper 
           under HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Control Panel\Desktop
Step 5: Choose Modify and paste the Image Path under Value data and Click 
             OK
 

Step 6: Close the Regedit Tool window and Signout from Windows
 
Step 7: Now Sign In again to windows, Wallpaper is Changed!
